- Auto correction: alt+enter
- Create variable from selected code: ctrl+alt+V
- Open/Close projects window: alt+1
- Find attribute declaration: ctrl+B
- Rename/Refactor code in the whole class: ctrl+alt+shift+T

- Most recent opened files: ctrl+E
- Search classes: shift + shift
- Search in the code: ctrl+shift+F

- Show all places of variable: alt + F7
- Format code: ctrl + alt +L
- Jump into errors when multiple errors: F2
- run anywhere: ctrl+ctrl

